  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Personal Assistant (Travel required, HR Function)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide day-to-day <strong>personal and business support</strong> to senior management, including coordination of meetings, schedules, and follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Support <strong>HR-related matters</strong>, including liaising with HR consultants, handling sensitive information, and assisting with people-related coordination</p></li><li><p>Attend <strong>business meetings</strong> and manage related administrative tasks, as well as support personal errands when required</p></li><li><p>Coordinate <strong>local and overseas travel arrangements</strong>, including logistics, itineraries, and accommodations (travel up to 7–10 days per month)</p></li><li><p>Act as a trusted point of contact, exercising discretion and sound judgment in handling confidential matters</p></li><li><p>Manage multiple tasks simultaneously while meeting <strong>tight deadlines</strong> and working under pressure</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Background in <strong>Human Resources</strong>, preferably with exposure to <strong>HR consulting</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal skills with the ability to <strong>read people and situations</strong> effectively</p></li><li><p>Fast learner who thrives in a <strong>high-pressure, dynamic environment</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd      </p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Lee Jun Siong (Johnson)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24120242</p>",
